so-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto"><font face="Times New Roman"><b><span style="COLOR: black">Trash:</span></b><span style="COLOR: black"><p /></span></font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto"><span style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Georgia">Yeah, yeah, I know this is a little bit late, but I’ve been really busy lately.  Hopefully my memory will guide me as I write up the events of last Tuesday (almost a week ago…).  </span><span style="COLOR: black"><p /></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto"><span style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Georgia">            Well, the fifth running of the So Happy It\'s Tuesday Hash House Harriers brought out absolutely no virgins, a first for the SHIT.  We did however, welcome a bunch of visitors to our humble group.  Seems <b>Whine-n-Cheese</b> will be taking class on Wednesdays and therefore missing OTH4 for a while.  <b>Andhowsherbush</b> was especially happy to hear this, because he can now be FRB at OTH4.  That’s not really saying too much for Tiny Bushes, who was also visiting from OTH4.  We also had <b>Done in 6 Seconds</b> from Everyday is Wednesday, <b>Hop-on-Cock</b> (who got gum stuck in her hair) from </span><state><place><span style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Georgia">Mount Vernon</span></place></state><span style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Georgia">, and <b>MIC-Och Shoots Blanks</b> and <b>Target Practice</b> (with their flour sniffing dog) from White House.</span><span style="COLOR: black"><p /></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto"><span style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Georgia">            <b>Shellacking the Bishop</b>, the smartest guy I know, was FRB last week.  For his efforts, he was awarded the coveted FRB Cone.  He carried it under his arm (not like some people who carry it over their shoulder and let the base hit them in the ass during the entire run) like a pro.  Next week, <b>Whine-n-Cheese</b> or <b>Tiny Bushes</b> will have the honor.</span><span style="COLOR: black"><p /></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto"><span style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Georgia">            Hares were away, promptly at </span><time minute="0" hour="19"><span style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Georgia">7:00pm</span></time><span style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Georgia">, with two virgin hares along for the ride.  Start thinking about names for the first three hashers to be named at the SHIT—Just <b>Stephanie</b>, Just <b>Shelley</b>, and Just<b> Norland</b> are all getting named on Tuesday!</span><span style="COLOR: black"><p /></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto"><span style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Georgia">            Trail was really good, very well marked and somewhat short.  Us walkers had a good old time, peeing on trail and complaining about the cold.  We kept seeing <b>Obese</b> with the blinking hashit, apparently he was not on trail but he did manage to not lose the hashit.</span><span style="COLOR: black"><p /></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto"><span style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Georgia">            We circled up, honored the violators, swung low and headed to Kirkpatricks.  If you didn’t go, you missed the rock star that was performing.  He had the best 80s rock voice, I swear.  You also missed the hashit holder, <b>Andhowsherbush</b>, dancing on a table wearing black socks and red nail polish.  </span><span style="COLOR: black"><p /></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto"><span style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Georgia">            Until we meet again…Tuesday, in Man-asses, where your hares will be OTH4ers <b>Grease Monkey</b> and <b>Dixie Queen</b>.  Hopefully the on-on-on will be at that shitty bar that has mice and roaches that we love so much!  See ya then!</span><span style="COLOR: black"><p /></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto"><span style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Georgia">                        <b>ON-ON!  Tupperware</b></span><span style="COLOR: black"><p /></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto"><b><span style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Georgia"> </span></b><span style="COLOR: black"><p /></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto"><span style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Georgia">P. S. Sign up for the email list, go to <a href="http://www.sohappyhash.com/"><span style="COLOR: blue">www.sohappyhash.com</span></a> and click on the little purple “YAHOO” icon on the bottom left.</span><span style="COLOR: black"><p /></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto"><span style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Georgia"> </span><span style="COLOR: black"><p /></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto"><span style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Georgia">P.S. again:  Tupperware’s 1<sup>st</sup> Anal “Tour de Basura Blanca” (that’s Tour De White Trash for you gringos) Pub Crawl will be held on October 29.  Just a heads up, cost will be $6 if you are wearing a costume and $10 if you are dressing like yourself.</span><span style="COLOR: black"><p /></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto"><span style="COLOR: black"><font face="Times New Roman"> <p /></font></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto"><b><span style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Georgia">Violations:</span></b><span style="COLOR: black"><p /></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto"><span style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Georgia">     Birthdays:                              O-69</span><span style="COLOR: black"><p /></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto"><span style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Georgia">     Forgetting Birthday:            Hood Whorenament</span><span style="COLOR: black"><p /></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto"><span style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Georgia">     Rico Suave:                            Butt Master (wearing a really tight shirt)</span><span style="COLOR: black"><p /></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto"><span style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Georgia">     Grimace Butt:                       Cunning Runt</span><span style="COLOR: black"><p /></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto"><span style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Georgia">     Whining:                                Shellacking the Bishop &amp; Vominatrix</span><span style="COLOR: black"><p /></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt 2in; TEXT-INDENT: -2in; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto"><span style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Georgia">     P.O.T:                                     O69, Pencil Dick, Tupperware, Just Stephanie, Dual Floppies, and AirTight Seal</span><span style="COLOR: black"><p /></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto"><span style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Georgia">     Landing Aircraft:                  Bad Dog</span><span style="COLOR: black"><p /></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto"><span style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Georgia">     FRB Envy:                             AndHowsHerBush</span><span style="COLOR: black"><p /></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto"><span style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Georgia">     Racing:                                   Dual Floppies and Tupperware</span><span style="COLOR: black"><p /></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto"><span style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Georgia">     Being a Grumpy Gus:          Obese</span><span style="COLOR: black"><p /></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto"><span style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Georgia">     Lost Shoes:                            Tupperware</span><span style="COLOR: black"><p /></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto"><span style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Georgia">     Shaving:                                 Field of Cream and Obese (both shave chests and pubes)</span><span style="COLOR: black"><p /></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto"><span style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Georgia">     Stealing Hashit:                    Hood Whorenament and Whine-n-Cheese</span><span style="COLOR: black"><p /></span></p><p><span style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Georgia; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">     Losing Hashit:                       Obese</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Arial"><p /></span></p>