 black"><p /></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto"><span style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Georgia"> </span><span style="COLOR: black"><p /></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto"><span style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Georgia">                        ON-ON!  Tupperware</span><span style="COLOR: black"><p /></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto"><span style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Georgia"> </span><span style="COLOR: black"><p /></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto"><span style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Georgia">P. S. Sign up for the email list, go to <a href="http://www.sohappyhash.com/"><span style="COLOR: blue">www.sohappyhash.com</span></a> and click on the little purple “YAHOO” icon on the bottom left.</span><span style="COLOR: black"><p /></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto"><span style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Georgia">P.S. again:  Tupperware’s 1st Anal “Tour de Basura Blanca” (that’s Tour De White Trash for you gringos) Pub Crawl will be held on October 29.  Just a heads up, cost will be $6 if you are wearing a costume and $10 if you are dressing like yourself.</span><span style="COLOR: black"><p /></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto"><span style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Georgia">P.S.S. again:  We still need hares, see <b>Mini Barbarino</b> to sign up!</span><span style="COLOR: black"><p /></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto"><b><span style="COLOR: black">Violations:</span></b><span style="COLOR: black"><p /></span><