(91, 77, '<P class=MsoTitle style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt"><U><FONT face="Georgia, Times New Roman, Times, Serif">Trail # 77 Michael Jordan and Yasser Arafat Birthday Celebration<?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" /><o:p></o:p></FONT></U></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: center" align=center><U><FONT size=3><FONT face="Georgia, Times New Roman, Times, Serif">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></U></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><FONT size=3><FONT face="Georgia, Times New Roman, Times, Serif">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><FONT face="Georgia, Times New Roman, Times, Serif" size=3>It had been a long time since the <B>SH*T</B> had set foot in this part of Sterling but who can say no to a hash that celebrates the birthdays of Michael Jordan <U>AND</U> Yasser Arafat!<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>We had the honor of having <B>Test Tube Baby</B> and <B>Just Andy</B> Hare our return with the walking assistance of <B>Tupperware</B> so we felt pretty privileged to be back in town.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>It', ''),
