(114, 80, '\r\n<p><strong><u><font size="5" face="Georgia, Times New Roman, Times, Serif">Visiting Trash</font></u></strong></p>\r\n<p><font size="5" face="Georgia"><!--StartFragment --><font size="2">OK, so everything is kicking ass so far on our Trash In DC (We Came, We Cummed, We Cum-quered) roadtrip... last night we hashed with the wankers at So Happy Its Tuesday (SHIT H3).  In a hash write up on their website they posted that they were the &quot;Bad boys&quot; of DC hashing... we came to show them what bad is.  So here is the recap of Trash In DC part 1 <br /><br />1) Moremen The Better and Dick Snail were called into the circle as vistors and asked why were were here; Moremen: &quot;To drink all your beer&quot;, Dick Snail: &quot;To steal all your women.&quot; <br /><br />2)We got accused of wearing the gayest t-shirts ever (don\'t worry pictures will eventually follow)and got sent into the circle, we then reminded the GM that we had earlier gave him a t-shirt!  See how quickly the accuser can become the accused! <br /><br />3) Moremen got beat by a girl...   and not in the wierdo sexual way. <br /><br />4) I shit you not, this is a direct quote from a named SHIT H3 hashers &quot;What does YBF stand for?&quot; then followed by &quot;oh, does that mean we are on trail?&quot;  ...I can\'t make up shit this funny. <br /><br />5) Another shit hasher did an impression of a retard, it looked oddly similar to how Dick Snail runs. <br /><br />6) As a gift for upping the Shit hash by 5 points, the GM gave Moremen and Snail a SHIT T-shirt...   ...size XXL.  I know I have put on some weight lately, but this is ridiculous!  I could smuggle a whole family across the border in it.  (boo, slighlt racist/insensitive comment...  lighten up fucker) <br /><br />7) The Rise Of The Machines was apparent, when cellphones gained artifical intelligence and reprogrammed thereselves to say &quot;Trash Rules&quot; and speak all menu options in Spanish.  ...if only Arnold was not to busy ruining California to save us. <br /><br />8) Apparently, hanging out with Moremen and Dick Snail is more fun than 4 orgasms!  (what can I say, we got the skillz to pay da billz) <br /><br />9) DC is known for its gangs and hard core street life, and we were first hand witnesses for a drive by!  ...a drive by mooning that is! <br /><br />10) What could be a better use of bandwith than porn or bloody penguin baseball?  Check out </font><a href="http://www.beerday.net/hash" class="moz-txt-link-abbreviated"><font size="2">www.beerday.net/hash</font></a><font size="2"> <br /><br />Dick Snail <br />Fear The Snail <br /></font></font></p>', '/ipw-web/gallery/80'),
