(437, 151, 'From White Kane\'s blog: <br /><br /><div class="entry"><p>So another weekend, another camping trip.<br /><img height="250" src="http://elevatorfish.com/pics/bbq01/IMG_1321.jpg" width="300" /><br />This time at Fire in the cornhole &amp; Sideshow Boobs place. Here is the weekend in a nutshell, we hashed, had a cookout, listened to live enterntainment and the back patio and by the bonfire. The place we stayed had a ton of really cool swings all over the property.<br /><img height="300" src="http://elevatorfish.com/pics/bbq01/IMG_1304.jpg" width="250" /><br />The main one swung over a creek bed ravine and was a total rush.<br /><img src="http://elevatorfish.com/pics/bbq01/swing.gif" /><br />The weekend was so much fun that I had to go an injure Sailor.<br />After swinging a few times,<br /><img height="250" src="http://elevatorfish.com/pics/bbq01/IMG_1310.jpg" width="300" /><br />I noticed Sailor was watching the fun, after some persuading I talked him into doing it himself (First mistake).<br /><img height="300" src="http://elevatorfish.com/pics/bbq01/IMG_1309.jpg" width="250" /><br />He swang back and forth a few times, said how fun it was then inquired as to how he could get off of the swing. To which I replied', '/images/151/album.php'),
