(418, 149, '<p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: center" align="center"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><u><span style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt">Trail # 149 – An Udderly, SH<personname w:st="on">*</personname>T-y, Trashy Trail<p /></span></u></b></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: center" align="center"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><u><span style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt"><p><span style="TEXT-DECORATION: none"> </span></p></span></u></b></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt">Hares: Dick Trashy, So Hot I’ll Turn U Gay, Udder Ho, Just John C &amp; Lube Me up Scotty</p><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><p> </p></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt">Trashy had this idea of all of us getting together and running a bunch of idiotic wankers around the Fairfax/Chantilly county.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">  </span>SHITU, Lube and I thought it was perfect, so we put aside our differences, gathered forces and created the greatest rock band in the world! </p><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><p> </p></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt">Unfortunately the band was short lived so after our first practice we decided to scout this trail that Trashy had in his pocket.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">  </span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><p> </p></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt">Returners: C<personname w:st="on">*</personname>ckspur the Friendly Host, Dick trashy, everybody Got Some, Everyone’s On My A$$, Ewe Sheep F’er, Just Amanda, Just Heather, <personname w:st="on">Lactose</personname> Tolerant, Your Honor I Suck C<personname w:st="on">*</personname>ck, Little C<personname w:st="on">*</personname>ck That Won’t, Seed Me After Class, Split Pussinality, Tupperware</p><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><p> </p></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt">The gathering began at one of the multiple soccer fields in Fairfax/Chantilly with a quickly growing group of newcomers, oldcomers and one solo cummer (that we know of)</p><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><p> </p></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt">Virgins: Just Brian, Just Neo, Just John C</p><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><p> </p></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt">Anaversary: ASSume the Position (7), Golden Showers (28), Mr. Softie (25), Pot Hole (28)</p><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><p> </p></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt">Things got off to a great start as SHITU took care of sign in and the rest of the Hares had a pre-trail beer.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">  </span></p>', '/images/149/album.php'),
