 </span><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal">Our Own Vanna</b> and <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal">Naval Jelly</b> seemed to enjoy themselves, as did <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal">Ewe Sheep F<personname w:st="on">*</personname>cker</b> and his partner in crime <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal">Crotch Rot</b>.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">  </span>We even had <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal">Holy Mackrell</b> and <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal">Lack O Nucki</b> make it for a beer and some chips.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">  </span>All-in-all everything worked well, just a little longer and hotter than expected, but it is the <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal">SH<personname w:st="on">*</personname>T</b> so what else would you expect?</p><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><p> </p></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt">Until next time,</p><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt">On Out</p><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt">Udder Ho.</p><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><p> </p></p>', ''),
