(1355, 732, '<p style="margin-bottom: 6px; color: rgb(20, 24, 35); font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; line-height: 19.32px;">Trail #731: Kick ATWI out of VA Trail - Oakton, VA (2016-03-22)<br>Hares: All the Way In, Dr Cockulus, The Great White MILF<br>Hashit: Parents Weakend, because the child is not his.</p><p style="margin-top: 6px; margin-bottom: 6px; color: rgb(20, 24, 35); font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; line-height: 19.32px;">Goodbyes are always hard, unless it&apos;s High School Graduation, then it&apos;s more like, "see you in hell, twat" And, years later, you ALWAYS run into the scum of your high school graduating class, like the coke dealer who expects you to give him a free chocolate milk while you&apos;re working at Panera, whil<span class="text_exposed_show" style="display: inline;">e you&apos;re wearing that stupid Panera hat and apron, just trying to save money for all the beer you plan to consume in the coming academic year. That chocolate milk is organic gold, you can&apos;t just give it away. But you know who you never run into again? All the girls that you realized you had crushes on but were too busy being in denial. I&apos;ve been patiently waiting to suggest having "an old school sleepover party, just like old times" for the last TEN YEARS. Maybe one day, Jennifer, maybe one day...</span></p><div class="text_exposed_show" style="display: inline; color: rgb(20, 24, 35); font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; line-height: 19.32px;"><p style="margin-bottom: 6px;">We got to trail start - it was nice weather, we had a good crowd. Lush has a sister she doesn&apos;t know about, and the sister was there and even provided the venue for beer check. I made a note of the address so we can go back and sneak in the hot tub/live in the garage for a while. We ran through a graveyard and I&apos;m pretty sure we&apos;re all haunted now. We ran around a high school and I did some hurdles, just like in high school, but I didn&apos;t eat shit this time. Trail ended at Milf&apos;s house and ATWI and Milf supplied us with an array of good food to shove into my mouth. We may have scared away another one of Milf&apos;s Au Pair&apos;s, so I would say it was successful trail.</p><p style="margin-top: 6px; margin-bottom: 6px;">Some violations happened, but I don&apos;t remember any of them. Parents Weakend got the hashit because he&apos;s about to have a child and will probably disappear from hashing for a while. Obviously, his priorities are just not in the right place. More importantly, we all gathered around to tell ATWI how much we don&apos;t appreciate all of his shiggy trails, his willingness to always lend a helping hand, all of the good food he cooks for us, his sexual generosity, his hashing wisdom and knowledge, all of his songs, and blah blah blah. I mean, how pretentious can someone be?</p><p style="margin-top: 6px; margin-bottom: 6px;">While I&apos;ve only been with S.H.I.T for the last year, most can speak at length about ATWI&apos;s awesomeness/awfulness much better than I. I&apos;m sure we will run into him sometime in the future, just like those in your graduating class that never go away. For those that regret their missed opportunity to experience ATWI&apos;s sexual healing ...you will never see him again.</p><p style="margin-top: 6px; margin-bottom: 6px;">"See you in hell, ATWI!"</p></div>', ''),
